PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?dog ?dogLabel ?age WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 ; wdt:P569 ?birthDate ; wdt:P570 ?deathDate .
  BIND( year( ?deathDate ) - year( ?birthDate ) AS ?age )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?age )
LIMIT 2

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?game ?gameLabel ?releaseDate WHERE {
  ?game wdt:P178 wd:Q677273 .
  ?game wdt:P577 ?releaseDate .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?game rdfs:label ?gameLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?gameLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?releaseDate
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

  wd:Q25369 wdt:P166 wd:Q674359 ; p:P166 [ pq:P585 ?year ] .
